# 1994–95 snooker world rankings

1994–95 snooker world rankings: The professional world rankings for snooker players in the 199495 season are listed below.
Stephen Hendry retained the top ranking for the fifth consecutive year. It was the first season in the elite "top 16" for Ronnie O'Sullivan, Peter Ebdon, Tony Drago and Joe Swail. For the first time since 1978, Dennis Taylor was not amongst the top 16.
